{
  "stem": "14091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That food would be sent, like cattle, they would liquidate that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the Germans decided that this is the only way, that they must liquidate the partisans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they arranged a very thorough combing of the woods-- also by planes and by artillery-- to get rid of the partisans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The partisans ran towards a different way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the Jews who were hiding didn't know anywhere to run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they were very acquainted with the woods and the vicinity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I among them, we start running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was a very big family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were actually two families.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the-- the shooting, the bombing, it was-- I never thought that we will survive that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But this wasn't as-- I-- I wasn't that upset, because I thought, if I'm going to be killed by a bomb, it's better than running like a-- like a scared animal and being shot by the Germans and this.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we ran.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, we all ran, and we came to the swamps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all, again, got into the swamps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans never came there, neither the-- the local collaborators.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never went to the swamps, because they thought they-- nobody could survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when in need, you can.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we were in the swamps for-- until it got very quiet and it-- they retreated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we got out of there, and again, we had the problem of cleaning ourselves and this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of the men, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]. ?] Although he was a huge man, but his nickname was [NON-ENGLISH], because he was so huge, so they made him that he's tiny.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he brought us to an abandoned partisan location where they had-- where they had those dugouts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
